Issue 5.4
Location: Section IV.B.iii references to Figure 1
Type: Structural
Severity: Minor
Description: Section IV.B.iii states "Performance comparison across codecs is presented in Figure~\ref{fig:unified_codecs}." The section is titled "Visual Analysis of Results," which implies the primary content is visual, yet the figure analysis is primarily textual. Additionally, the figure reference appears early in the subsection before the substantive discussion, but the figure itself (floating with [!ht]) may render after the section depending on page layout. The placement should be verified in the final compiled PDF to ensure figures appear close to their first reference.
